Package: scQCFilter
Type: Package
Title: Single-Cell Quality Control Filtering and Multi-Dimensional Analysis
Version: 2.1.1
Author: Zhijun Feng
Maintainer: Zhijun Feng <xiaoqqjun@sina.com>
Description: A comprehensive R package for quality control filtering of
    single-cell RNA-seq data with three-dimensional analysis (parameters,
    groups, and samples). Generates automated HTML reports with pre-filtering
    QC distribution plots, supports multi-parameter comparison, and provides
    intelligent parameter recommendations. New in v1.0.0: pre-filtering QC
    distribution visualization with percentile thresholds (2.5%, 5%, 95%, 97.5%).
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.0
Imports:
    Seurat,
    ggplot2,
    dplyr,
    tidyr,
    ComplexHeatmap,
    patchwork,
    png,
    grDevices,
    graphics
Suggests:
